    public class TripleFormattedPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements java.awt.event.KeyListener
    Class providing an easy way to use three fields together. Usefull for three coordinates informations (X, Y, Z or U, Th, K, or anything else)
    Author:
    Alan Guitard
    See Also:
    KeyListener, TripleLabelizedPanel, Serialized Form
